message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your business. Given its value and the impact it could have on your operations, I am offering it to you at a special introductory price of $12,000. This represents an excellent opportunity to acquire a high-quality asset at a competitive rate. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing this further or if there's any way I can assist you in making a decision.
